claw.tatsu.xcodeml.xnode.common

Class XcodeProgram

  • java.lang.Object
    • claw.tatsu.xcodeml.xnode.common.Xnode
      • claw.tatsu.xcodeml.xnode.common.XcodeML
        • claw.tatsu.xcodeml.xnode.common.XcodeProgram

  • public class XcodeProgram
extends XcodeML
    The XcodeProgram represents the XcodeProgram (2) element in XcodeML intermediate representation. Elements: ( typeTable, globalSymbols, globalDeclarations ) - Required: - typeTable (XtypeTable) - globalSymbols (XsymbolTable) - globalDeclarations (XglobalDeclTable) Attributes: - Optional: compiler-info (text), version (text), time (time), language (text), source (text)
    Author:
    clementval
